Framed Prints

Bring a touch of history into your home with our exquisite framed print of Lady Isabel Burton as a bride, painted by Louis Desanges. This stunning artwork is taken from the book "The Life of Captain Sir Richard Burton, Volume I," authored by Lady Burton herself, and published in 1893. Add a sense of elegance and sophistication to your decor with this beautiful piece, which captures the essence of a bygone era. A must-have for history enthusiasts and art collectors alike.

Photo Prints

Bring history to life with this exquisite photographic print of Lady Isabel Burton, painted by Louis Desanges in 1893. This captivating image is taken from the pages of "The Life of Captain Sir Richard Burton, Volume I," penned by Lady Burton herself. Witness the radiant beauty and elegance of Lady Burton as she adorns her bridal attire, captured in this stunning artwork. Add a touch of rich history to your home decor or office space with this timeless piece from Media Storehouse's range of photographic prints.

Poster Prints

Step back in time with our exquisite Lady Isabel Burton As A Bride poster print. This stunning artwork, painted by Louis Desanges and originally featured in "The Life of Captain Sir Richard Burton, Volume I" by Isabel Burton, captures the elegance and beauty of Lady Burton on her wedding day in 1831. Bring the rich history of Sir Richard Francis Burton's life into your home or office with this beautiful and intricately detailed poster print. A must-have for history enthusiasts and art lovers alike.

Jigsaw Puzzles

Add a touch of history to your puzzle collection with the Media Storehouse Jigsaw Puzzle featuring Lady Isabel Burton as a bride. This beautiful puzzle showcases a painting by Louis Desanges, taken from The Life of Captain Sir Richard Burton, Volume I, by Isabel Burton herself. Dive into the past as you piece together this intricate and captivating puzzle, bringing the elegant portrait of Lady Isabel to life. A perfect gift for history enthusiasts or puzzle lovers alike.
